author: Fr. Matt Ainsely & Fr. David Bumsted
name: The Sacristy
description:
Join with Fr. Matt and Fr. David as they seek to learn, discuss, and exult in the faith delivered once for all to the saints as it has been passed down in) the Anglican Tradition.

Fr. Matt is the vicar of All Souls Episcopal Church, a church plant in Horizon West, FL. All Souls is temporarily meeting at the Church of the Messiah in Winter Garden, FL. For more information;
www.allsoulsfl.org
